**APEX CODE TO CALCULATE LEAP YEAR**

===============================================

public class leapyear 
{
    public static void leap()
    {
        integer y = 2015;
        if(math.mod(y,4)==0)
        {
            system.debug('Is a Leap Year');
        }
        else
        {
            system.debug('Not a Leap Year');
        }
    }
    
}

**TO EXECUTE OUTPUT USE THE FOLLOWING COMMAND**

leapyear.leap();

===============================================
